document_data.Slave Vats of the Yuan-ti:
: ''By [[Jason Kuhl]], illustrated by [[Terry Dykstra]], Cartography by [[Diesel]].'' '''p. 10-27'''
[[File:Mere-of-Dead-Men-Slave-Vats-of-the-Yuan-ti.png|thumb|left|100px]]
This adventure is part 1 of the "[[Mere of Dead Men]]" series and involves an exploration of the [[Wolfhill House]] overlooking the Mere and encounters with the [[yuan-ti]]. Module for 4-6 PC's of levels 3-5.{{Dusup|69/Slave Vats of the Yuan-ti}}

document_data.Sleep of Ages:
{{Main|Dungeon magazine 69/Sleep of Ages}}
: ''By [[Eric L. Boyd]], illustrated by [[Stephen Schwartz]], Cartography by [[Craig Zipse]].'' '''p. 50-76'''
[[File:Bleucorundum.png|thumb|left|100px]]
This adventure is set in the [[Lands of Intrigue]] and involves the [[beholders]] of the [[Lake of Steam region]] known as the [[Alimir Hive]]. The adventure revolves around an archeological search within the [[Omlarandin Mountains]] and a rescue mission to retrieve the [[Gnome|gnomish]] scholar who went missing on the way there.{{Dusup|69/Sleep of Ages}}
